pline borders.The present volumes are the outcome of two conferences in Rome 2008 and at Metochi (Lesbos) 2009.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aBaptismxHistoryyEarly church, ca. 30-600vCongresses. 0aBaptismxJudaismxHistoryvCongresses. 0aLustrationsxHistoryvCongresses. 4aInitiation. 4aRitus. 4aTaufe. 4aWaschung. 7aRELIGION / Christian Rituals & Practice / General.2bisacsh  aAblution.  aBaptism.  aInitiation.  aRite.1 aAasgaard, Reidar, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aApostolos-Cappadona, Diane, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aAssmann, Jan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBecker, Eve-Marie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBetz, Hans Dieter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBlomkvist, Vemund, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBrandt, Olof, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBrändle, Rudolf, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBurns, J. Patout, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aByrskog, Samuel, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDay, Juliette, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEkenberg, Anders, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFreyne, Seán, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGraf, Fritz, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHartman, Lars, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHartvigsen, Kirsten Marie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHellholm, Christer, eed